6ee23218f2240677b4a3e9042a77e52983028929111a4c4b0902d032ed5b845ad246e780a7625059d18c7321089f44850f4a597030997f2171f7fc49c62b7607  0001-setup-disk-fix-find_efi_size-for-multidisk.patch
